text:
Tried the Triple Delight Combo Set.
The portion is huge.
Chicken chop, pork chop and sausage taste good, though the fish taste abit bland.
Newly open likely around dec 2024. Generous serving portion for the price. Food is good too.
Had the pork chop with black pepper sauce. Big portion. Taste was nice. Presentation could improve though.
2nd time here. This time takeaway. Very big portion the HM1 Hainanese Chicken Chop here. $8.20.
Giant portions with excellent food. Try the Mac and cheese.
